<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <%- include("partials/head", {
    pageTitle: "Software Engineering and Web Development"
  }) %>

  <body>
    <%- include("partials/nav") %>

    <main>
      <section class="page-title">
        <p class="eyebrow">HW 4: Express</p>
        <h1>Software Engineering and Web Development</h1>

        <p>
          Learn how planning, design, programming, and testing
          work together to create useful software.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="hero">
        <article>
          <h2>Overview</h2>

          <p>
            Software engineering is the process of designing,
            building, testing, and maintaining software. Web
            development is one part of software engineering that
            focuses on websites and web applications.
          </p>

          <p>
            A good website is not only about writing code. It also
            needs planning, design, testing, and maintenance. These
            steps help developers create websites that are useful,
            organized, and easy to use.
          </p>
        </article>

        <figure>
          <img
            src="/img/overview.jpg"
            alt="Overview of web development"
          >
        </figure>
      </section>

      <section class="cards">
        <article class="card">
          <span class="card-number">01</span>
          <h3>Planning</h3>

          <p>
            Developers plan the structure and goals before writing
            code.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <span class="card-number">02</span>
          <h3>Design</h3>

          <p>
            Design helps users understand and enjoy the website.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <span class="card-number">03</span>
          <h3>Testing</h3>

          <p>
            Testing helps find errors before the website is
            published.
          </p>
        </article>
      </section>
    </main>

    <%- include("partials/footer") %>
  </body>
</html>